sequenceDiagram
    participant Manifest as plugin.json（可选）
    participant Loader as createPluginFromPath
    participant FS as 文件系统
    participant Consumer as loadPluginCommands

    Manifest-->>Loader: commands: "./src/cmds/" （覆盖）
    Loader->>FS: 清单有声明 → 跳过探测
    Loader->>Consumer: plugin.commandsPath = "./src/cmds/"

    Note over Manifest: 或：清单无 commands 字段
    Loader->>FS: pathExists("commands/")
    FS-->>Loader: true
    Loader->>Consumer: plugin.commandsPath = "commands/"

    FS-->>Loader: false（目录不存在）
    Note over Consumer: plugin.commandsPath = undefined → 不加载命令
